Installation for Dokuwiki V0.1 on PHProjekt 5.2.x:


1. If the PHProjekt installation is not on the Webserver DocumentRoot, you must change in the follow 
    files some paths:

conf/dokuwiki.php
  set DOKU_BASE to path from DocumentRoot to addons.
   one example: phprojekt is installed under "http://localhost/special/phprojekt/" than
    change the DOKU_BASE to '/special/phprojekt/addons/'
lib/tpl/default/design.css
  change all url statements to the full document path
lib/styles/styles.css
  change all url statements to the full document path

2. To restrict the access on one phprojekt group change follow files:
doku.php
  Uncomment the line 16.
dokuwiki.inc.php
  define the 'PHPDW_PERMIT_GROUP' with the ID of the group.
   You can find the ID in the database table gruppen from phprojekt.
